Class AbstractContainerHelper.UIContextWrap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.UIContextDelegate
      • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.container.AbstractContainerHelper.UIContextWrap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UIContext, Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractContainerHelper

    public static class AbstractContainerHelper.UIContextWrap
extends UIContextDelegate
    This class exists because we'd like to simulate clustering while still being able to use the UIContext as the synchronization lock when servicing a request.
